    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">macOS如何下载安装Zotero</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Zotero最初是基于Firefox浏览器的插件，现在可以基于桌面独立安装，支持多种常见操作系统，如Linux，iOS，macOS和Windows等。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
        <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">本节主要以Safari浏览器为例，介绍如何在macOS系统上下载安装Zotero。</p>
        </context>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">进入Zotero官网<xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="https://www.zotero.org/" scope="external"/>。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">点击页面中部红色背景"Download"按钮，如下图所示：</cmd>
                <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image class="- topic/image " href="" id="image_k1w_jtg_mdc" placement="inline" width="100"/></info>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在跳转的新页面中找到左方"Zotero 7 for Mac"模块，点击蓝底白字"Download"按钮，如图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="" id="image_m4h_ztg_mdc" placement="inline" width="157"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在弹出的"你要允许'www.zotero.org'上的下载吗"对话框中选择"允许"，然后等待下载。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">下载完成后，双击Zotero的dmg文件，如图所示：<image class="- topic/image " href="" id="image_hvd_dwg_mdc" placement="inline" width="200"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">在弹出框中将左侧的"Zotero"图标拖拽到右侧的"Drage Here to Install"里，然后等待Zotero拷贝到应用程序。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">双击应用程序中Zotero图标以打开软件，如图所示<image class="- topic/image " href="" id="image_izm_rwg_mdc" placement="inline" width="100"/></cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">系统弹出对话框"'Zotero'是从互联网下载的App。您确定要打开它吗？"，请选择"打开"。</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">当弹出"欢迎来到Zotero"页面时，表明已成功下载安装，此时官网会有如下提示：<image class="- topic/image " href="" id="image_nnq_gxg_mdc" placement="inline" width="300"/></cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
